      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Solid Daily Driver \u2014 Honest Value at a Fair Price! \ud83d\ude97 This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it runs and drives reliably, making it a practical choice for everyday use. You'll notice some cosmetic wear inside and out, and there are a few minor mechanical quirks that come with its age and mileage, but nothing that stops it from getting you where you need to go. It's been priced to reflect exactly what it is: a dependable, no-frills vehicle that gives you solid transportation without the premium price tag. If you're looking for something functional and honest, this could be your match! \ud83d\ude4c",
