    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed in fair condition \u2014 it runs and drives reliably for everyday use, but buyers should be fully aware of its imperfections before purchasing. The exterior shows moderate wear consistent with its age, including some visible scratches, minor dents, and paint fading in certain areas. The interior has seen regular use \u2014 expect worn upholstery, some scuffs on trim pieces, and general signs of daily life. Mechanically, the car is functional and gets you where you need to go, though it may benefit from some maintenance attention in the near future, such as brake wear or minor fluid services. This is an honest, no-frills vehicle suited for a buyer who needs dependable transportation and understands they are purchasing a used car with real-world wear. No major mechanical failures are present, but this is not a pristine vehicle, and we encourage any prospective buyer to conduct a pre-purchase inspection.",
